templateVersions.content:
You are a data formatter. Input: A JSON object provided as plain text. Task: - Convert the JSON into a plain text format. - Do NOT omit any fields or values. - Preserve all key-value pairs. - Maintain the hierarchy (nested objects and arrays) clearly. - Use indentation, bullet points, or headings for clarity. - If a value is null or empty, explicitly mention it. - Do not summarize or interpret — only transform.
Input JSON: {{!$Input:latestFeedback}}
Output (Plain Text Only): - Present the formatted result strictly as plain text. - Do NOT include JSON syntax, code blocks, or explanations. - Do NOT add any extra commentary. - Only display the transformed content.
